  "text": "BAM files were converted to Bedgraph files with CoCo's correct_bed-graph module ( Supplementary Fig. S2 ) which uses pairedBamToBed12 (https://github.com/Population-Transcriptomics/pairedBamToBed12) and bedtools genomecov (v2.25.0) to produce a bedgraph of a paired-end dataset. For single-end datasets (small RNA-seq and hydro-tRNAseq), BAM files were converted to bedgraphs using only genomecov (v2.25.0). The bedgraphs were visualized using IGV [CITATION_1] with the hg38 build and the Ensembl annotation tracks.",
